在2013年12月31日時，'''[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]'''有人口7,245,677人<ref name="nsi.bg">{{cite web |url=http://www.nsi.bg/en/content/12094/%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%81%D1%81%D1%8A%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5/demographic-processes-2013-final-data |title=National statistical institute |publisher=Nsi.bg |date=2014-04-17 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |archive-date=2014-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419014710/http://www.nsi.bg/en/content/12094/%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%81%D1%81%D1%8A%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5/demographic-processes-2013-final-data |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保加利亞人口在1989年達到峰值，為9,009,018人。2011年人口普查時，保加利亞人口為7,364,570人<ref name=Census2011final>[http://www.nsi.bg/census2011/PDOCS2/Census2011final_en.pdf 2011 Bulgarian census] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FbykQLQG?url=http://www.nsi.bg/census2011/PDOCS2/Census2011final_en.pdf |date=20130403204835 |dateformat=iso }} (in English)</ref>。2012年，保加利亞的人類發展指數為0.782，屬於高發展度國家，在世界排名第57位<ref>[http://hdr.undp.org/en/reports/global/hdr2013/ Human Development Index 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://hdr.undp.org/en/reports/global/hdr2013/ |date=20181226004459 }}, Human development indices by the United Nations. Retrieved on 4 May 2013</ref>。按照新聞周刊的排名，保加利亞是世界第38位適合居住的國家<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsweek.com/2010/08/15/interactive-infographic-of-the-worlds-best-countries.html |title=Interactive Infographic of the World’s Best Countries |publisher=Newsweek.com |date=15 August 2010 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2010-09-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5sQWPP1Ay?url=http://www.newsweek.com/2010/08/15/interactive-infographic-of-the-worlds-best-countries.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保加利亞的大多數人口是保加利亞人，其次是[[土耳其|土耳其]]人和羅姆人。2011年時，保加利亞最多人信仰的宗教是東正教<ref>[http://censusresults.nsi.bg/Census/Reports/2/2/R10.aspx Population 2011 final results by Religion] {{Wayback|url=http://censusresults.nsi.bg/Census/Reports/2/2/R10.aspx |date=20120128054930 }} National Statistical Institute. Retrieved Sept 2012.</ref>。

==人口政策==
保加利亞人口的逐漸減少阻礙了經濟增長和福利的改善，為減輕負面後果而採取的管理措施不能解決問題的本質。 政府計劃2017-2021年是第一個旨在推翻這一趨勢的計劃。 該方案還確定了實現這一目標的優先手段：提高出生率的措施; 減少青年移民; 並製定符合保加利亞業務需求的現代移民政策的監管和機構能力。<ref>L. Ivanov. [https://www.researchgate.net/publication/319967867_Demographic_priorities_and_goals_of_the_Government_Program_2017-2021_in_Bulgarian_English_translation Demographic priorities and goals of the Government Program 2017–2021.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/319967867_Demographic_priorities_and_goals_of_the_Government_Program_2017-2021_in_Bulgarian_English_translation |date=20171025181535 }} Presentation at the round table ''Demographic Policies and Labour Mobility'' organized by the Ministry of Labour and Social Policy, and the State Agency for the Bulgarians Abroad. Sofia, 19 September 2017. 4 pp.</ref>

